ympic final guys, I am going to go for gold,\\\" said Woods, who had already picked up a bronze medal in the solo K1 category earlier in the Games.\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1867, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a moment\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1635}, {\"ngram\": \"gate\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1643}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 1686, \"to\": 1692}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic final guys\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1739}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1762, \"to\": 1766}, {\"ngram\": \"Woods\", \"from\": 1774, \"to\": 1779}, {\"ngram\": \"a bronze medal\", \"from\": 1807, \"to\": 1821}, {\"ngram\": \"the solo K1 category\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1845}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1857, \"to\": 1866}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have been in races where I have settled for silver, made the decision to play it safe.\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1958, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"races\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1890}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 1922}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 1941}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I did not want to do that.\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 1989, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's once every four years and I am a brave person in and out of the boat.\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 2064, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a brave person\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2040}, {\"ngram\": \"the boat\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2063}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I wanted to showcase that.\", \"from\": 2065, \"to\": 2091, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I went for it and got a little bit caught out.\\\"\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2139, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a little bit\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2126}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Clarke had looked set to defy the sport's inherent unpredictability as he swept comfortably through his quarter and semi-finals, albeit finishing top in 