tional_rugby_league_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2520, \"end\": 2532, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finn_Butcher\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Finn Butcher\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finn_Butcher\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finn_Butcher\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Clarke\", \"from\": 2373, \"to\": 2379}, {\"ngram\": \"an early advantage\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2502}, {\"ngram\": \"Clarke\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2567}, {\"ngram\": \"hot pursuit\", \"from\": 2615, \"to\": 2626}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will be honest with you, I came into this event wanting to win gold but that did not happen today,\\\" conceded Clarke, who was forced to settle for a fifth place finish last week when bidding to defend his Rio 2016 individual title.\", \"from\": 2629, \"to\": 2862, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this event\", \"from\": 2669, \"to\": 2679}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 2695, \"to\": 2699}, {\"ngram\": \"Clarke\", \"from\": 2741, \"to\": 2747}, {\"ngram\": \"a fifth place finish\", \"from\": 2778, \"to\": 2798}, {\"ngram\": \"his Rio 2016 individual title\", \"from\": 2832, \"to\": 2861}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have been in races where I have settled for silver, made the decision to play it safe.\", \"from\": 2864, \"to\": 2952, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"races\", \"from\": 2879, \"to\": 2884}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 2910, \"to\": 2916}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 2923, \"to\": 2935}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I did not want to do that.\", \"from\": 2953, \"to\": 2983, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's once every four years and I am a brave person in and out of the boat.\", \"from\": 2984, \"to\": 3058, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a brave person\", \"from\": 3020, \"to\": 3034}, {\"ngram\": \"the boat\", \"from\": 3049, \"to\": 3057}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I wanted to showcase that \\\"I am not disappointed in any way.\", \"from\": 3059, \"to\": 3120, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any way\", \"from\": 3111, \"to\": 3118}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A silver medal is absolutely massive, and I am very proud how I put myself about throughout the competition.\", \"from\": 3121, \"to\": 3229, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A silver medal\", \"from\": 3121, \"to\": 3135}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 3213, \"to\": 3228}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was quite off-putting to have that straight off the ramp but you have to deal with these things and I think I refocused pretty well.\\\"\", \"from\": 3230, \"to\": 3366, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"quite off-putting\", \"from\": 3237, \"to\": 3254}, {\"ngram\": \"the ramp\", \"from\": 3281, \"to\": 3289}, {\"ngram\": \"these things\", \"from\": 3316, \"to\": 3328}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Woods' team-mate Mallory Franklin finished second in her quarter-final but was one of a number of athletes to be disqualified after crossing the line for any number of infringements, including failing to correctly exit gates or not delivering the required eskimo roll at the right time.\", \"from\": 3368, \"to\": 3654, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3385, \"end\": 3401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mallory_Franklin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mallory Franklin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mallory_Franklin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mallory_Franklin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a number\", \"from\": 3454, \"to\": 3462}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 3466, \"to\": 3474}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 3509, \"to\": 3517}, {\"ngram\": \"any number\", \"from\": 3522, \"to\": 3532}, {\"ngram\": \"infringements\", \"from\": 3536, \"to\": 3549}, {\"ngram\": \"the required eskimo roll\", \"from\": 3611, \"to\": 3635}, {\"ngram\": \"the right time\", \"from\": 3639, \"to\": 3653}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kayakcross' short and often riotous battles brought the capacity crowd to its feet, and their reaction mirrored the response to the respective introductions of snowboard cross and ski cross in recent Winter Olympic cycles.\", \"from\": 3656, \"to\": 3878, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kayakcross' short and often riotous battles\", \"from\": 3656, \"to\": 3699}, {\"ngram\": \"the capacity crowd\", \"from\": 3708, \"to\": 3726}, {\"ngram\": \"its feet\", \"from\": 3730, \"to\": 3738}, {\"ngram\": \"their reaction\", \"from\": 3744, \"to\": 3758}, {\"ngram\": \"the response\", \"from\": 3768, \"to\": 3780}, {\"ngram\": \"the respective introductions\", \"from\": 3784, \"to\": 3812}, {\"ngram\": \"snowboard cross\", \"from\": 3816, \"to\": 3831}, {\"ngram\": \"ski cross\", \"from\": 3836, \"to\": 3845}, {\"ngram\": \"recent Winter Olympic cycles\", \"from\": 3849, \"to\": 3877}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both Woods and Clarke have no doubts about the impact of Olympic inclusion on a discipline that has often been disregarded by purists, but is evidently here to stay.\", \"from\": 3880, \"to\": 4045, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Both Woods\", \"from\": 3880, \"to\": 3890}, {\"ngram\": \"Clarke\", \"from\": 3895, \"to\": 3901}, {\"ngram\": \"no doubts\", \"from\": 3907, \"to\": 3916}, {\"ngram\": \"the impact\", \"from\": 3923, \"to\": 3933}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic inclusion\", \"from\": 3937, \"to\": 3954}, {\"ngram\": \"a discipline\", \"from\": 3958, \"to\": 3970}, {\"ngram\": \"purists\", \"from\": 4006, \"to\": 4013}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's had its ups and downs over the years and a lot of people have criticised it, saying it looks silly, but it's absolutely incredible, the atmosphere is insane and it's an amazing thing to be a part of,\\\" said Woods.\", \"from\": 4047, \"to\": 4265, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\"